.TH PQR 1 "2026-05-15" "v1.07" "PQR Sovereign Bridge"
.SH NAME
pqr \- Emergency management CLI for the PQR Sovereign Node
.SH SYNOPSIS
pqr [COMMAND] [PARAMS]
.SH DESCRIPTION
pqr is a WSL-native script that communicates with the PQR emergency bridge. It allows for out-of-band management of the swarm when the primary UI is unreachable.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
GET_SYSTEM_HEALTH
Returns the status, version, and uptime of the node.
.TP
LIST_RECENT_TICKETS
Retrieves the last 10 forensic tickets from the fabric.
.TP
TRIGGER_HEALING [ISSUE]
Manually initiates a healing loop for a specified issue.
.SH FILES
~/.env - Contains the GEMINI_API_KEY for authentication.
